ORIGINAL CONTRIBUTIONS BY BLUE ENGINE

The following components are original research and implementation
by Blue Chiou, developed independently of the iztro library:

CALCULATION CORRECTIONS:
- Complete four-transformations table (BlueVersion), correcting
  documented errors in iztro defaults across all 10 heavenly stems
  (critical correction: 庚-stem 天同科/天相忌, not iztro's default)
- Minor limit (小限) algorithm with verified starting positions
  and directional logic for all five elemental cycles (金/木/水/土/火)
  across yin/yang male/female configurations — replacing iztro's
  placeholder values and unverified starting points
- Eight Pillars start calculation (八字起運) with pre-1980 date
  bug fix for iztro's simplified/traditional Chinese key mismatch
- 8-tier brightness system (廟旺得利平不利陷不), extending iztro's
  6-tier system with verified auxiliary star brightness tables

ANALYTICAL SYSTEMS (not present in iztro):
- Bidirectional palace flying transformations (飛入/飛出)
- Self-transformation detection (自化) with source tracking
- Fortune-Restriction conflict detection v2 (祿忌交戰)
  with severity classification and palace-stem flying sources
- Triple-stem overlap detection (三干疊加)
- True solar time correction (30-city longitude database)
- Synastry analysis engine (/api/synastry)
- Flow year analysis engine (/api/flow)
- Classical formation detection (格局偵測)
- 斗君 calculation

These contributions represent the primary analytical value
of this repository. They are released under the same MIT
License as the project as a whole.
